♪Our tangled destiny
has trapped my heart in this life♪

2
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:36,060
♪Will I see you again in the next life♪

3
00:00:36,550 --> 00:00:43,500
♪Keep a piece of peach blossom
to remember the past and say goodbye♪

4
00:00:43,830 --> 00:00:49,920
♪But I still miss you
with tears in my eyes♪

5
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:57,250
♪Dig a hole, plant a tree, but the leaves
and flowers remind me of our past♪

6
00:00:57,480 --> 00:01:03,710
♪Sow the seeds of love,
but they bloom on the wrong path♪

7
00:01:04,340 --> 00:01:11,060
♪Move on, let go,
forget everything about you♪

8
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:18,220
♪Flowers fall on the road
where I fell in love with you♪

9
00:01:33,020 --> 00:01:37,660
=Stolen Love=

10
00:01:37,860 --> 00:01:40,700
=Episode 41=

11
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:44,280
Close the gate!

12
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:54,800
The front gate is blocked.

13
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,600
As for the one behind me,

14
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,440
if you want to get out,

15
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,440
pass me first.

16
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:03,120
Xiao Chuyi,

17
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,640
what tricks are you trying to play?

18
00:02:06,240 --> 00:02:08,200
Close the gate and beat the dogs.

19
00:02:09,480 --> 00:02:10,920
Can you beat us alone?

20
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,560
It won't take much effort

21
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,520
to kill a bunch of nasty rats.

22
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,040
Where are Yunxi and Che?

23
00:02:18,440 --> 00:02:20,800
Why are you asking about
my wife and my son?

24
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,160
They're my family!

25
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,880
I tortured Lady Zhou and killed

26
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,640
my cousin and the prince for her!

27
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:28,000
Don't blame these evil deeds on Yun!

28
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:33,040
You're always like this.

29
00:02:34,390 --> 00:02:37,000
You pretend to be weak
to make her care about you.

30
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,400
You appear to be a gentleman,

31
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:42,080
but in fact,
you're a cunning hypocrite.

32
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:44,560
Without Yun,
you'll still be an evil man.

33
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:49,280
You took care of my family
for seven years.

34
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,880
If you surrender now,

35
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,560
I'll spare your life.

36
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:57,840
Yunxi

37
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:00,640
will report this to His Majesty.

38
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:05,160
Then we'll kill Xiao Chuyi

39
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,200
and capture Yunxi.

40
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,000
Today,

41
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:11,440
I'll avenge my father

42
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:12,800
and my country!

43
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:23,400
Luesha,

44
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:27,760
I had mercy on you at Luoxia Ridge,

45
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:30,680
but you colluded with Zhou Yanyu
to destroy my country.

46
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:32,360
Today,

47
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:35,000
in the General's Mansion
of the Xiao Family,

48
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,280
I'll eliminate

49
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,440
all the traitors!

50
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:43,440
Kill him!

51
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:46,240
Kill him!

52
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:55,080
Kill him!

53
00:04:01,380 --> 00:04:04,180
(Noble in Character)

54
00:04:16,940 --> 00:04:22,180
(Blessing)

55
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:41,120
(Zhou Yanyu really
hid the Crown Prince here.)

56
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,520
Go!

57
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,200
Go!

58
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,200
Go!

59
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,120
How dare you trespass on the palace?

60
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,360
Here's the body of the Crown Prince.

61
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,320
I need to see His Majesty!

62
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,160
Let her in.

63
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:10,600
Go!

64
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,640
Chuyi!

65
00:09:03,860 --> 00:09:07,650
♪Across mountains♪

66
00:09:08,050 --> 00:09:11,110
♪Sad songs echo in the air♪

67
00:09:11,820 --> 00:09:15,370
♪Talking to the moon♪

68
00:09:15,370 --> 00:09:17,930
♪It changes like my mood♪

69
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:20,520
Yun.

70
00:09:20,530 --> 00:09:21,560
I've kept my promise.

71
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:23,040
You made it.

72
00:09:23,570 --> 00:09:26,050
♪We said goodbye♪

73
00:09:26,390 --> 00:09:29,860
♪Wishing you'd come back to me♪

74
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:33,570
♪But you never answered♪

75
00:09:33,940 --> 00:09:35,900
♪My cries♪

76
00:09:36,020 --> 00:09:37,640
♪And sighs♪

77
00:09:38,060 --> 00:09:40,920
♪Are buried in the snow♪

78
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:43,620
♪Horses run♪

79
00:09:43,780 --> 00:09:45,300
♪Into my dreams♪

80
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,560
