on a cold night♪

107
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:20,840
Help! Help!

108
00:12:21,560 --> 00:12:23,160
Help!

109
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:26,000
Help!

110
00:12:29,880 --> 00:12:31,240
Hold my hand!

111
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:34,480
♪You've stolen my heart♪

112
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:39,090
